api_list.name: Organization Provider Data GET
api_list.description: Provides clearbit data for an organization.  This can be used client side after validation and sent back in through a PATCH.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://grcschema.p.rapidapi.com/Organization/2/provider"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "grcschema.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

print(response.json())
